  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>
    This was originally a run at an October drawing challenge created by
    <a
      href="https://bsky.app/profile/albabbgg.bsky.social/post/3l44zgo24yl23"
      target="_blank">albabbgg</a
    >
    (link to the blue sky post, but they've posted across multiple platforms). I ended
    up using it to experiment with my comic making process. Because I didn't put a
    lot of planning into it, the character designs change at page 13. Very specifically,
    Bryony becomes a mouse. Oh well.
  </p>

  <p>
    In case something happens to the above link, below are the prompts for
    <strong>Cursed Relics 2024</strong>:
  </p>
  <ul style="margin-top: 0">
